## üí° Best Practices

1. **After code changes:** Always use Level 4 first
2. **After first full reload:** Use Level 1-3 for faster workflows
3. **For automated tests:** Use Level 3 (`forceReload()`)
4. **For UI changes only:** Use Level 1 (soft reload)
5. **When in doubt:** Check server logs to see which code is running

