## üîß Troubleshooting

### "Command timeout after 30000ms" when using toggleExtension()

**Cause:** Extension disabled for too long, API client timeout

**Solution:** Use Level 4 (manual remove/reload) instead

### "Registration failed: name must be non-empty string"

**Cause:** Chrome running old service worker code

**Solution:** Use Level 4 (Full Remove/Reload)

### forceReload() not working

**Cause:** Extension not connected to server OR running old code

**Solution:**
1. Check server logs to verify extension connected
2. If old code running, use Level 4 first
3. Then forceReload() will work

