| Level | Method | Commands Available | Speed | Reloads Service Worker | Loads Code from Disk | Automated | When Required |
|-------|--------|-------------------|-------|----------------------|---------------------|-----------|---------------|
| 0 | Fresh Start | freshStart (feature request) | üêå Very Slow | ‚úÖ Yes | ‚úÖ YES | ‚úÖ Yes | Clean slate / CI/CD |
