## üîÑ After Phase 0 Setup Complete

Once you've done Level 4 (Full Remove/Reload) ONE TIME with the new Phase 0 code:

**Regular development workflow:**
1. Edit background.js ‚Üí Level 4 (first time) or Level 1 (minor changes)
2. Edit popup.html ‚Üí Level 1 (soft reload)
3. Edit content scripts ‚Üí Level 1 (soft reload)
4. Test reload feature ‚Üí Level 2 or 3 (API methods)
5. Automated tests ‚Üí Level 3 (`forceReload()`)

**The key:** After the initial Level 4, faster methods work reliably.
